ygData.messageBody:
Once again, all this talk is making me want to go back to my necro. But
recently I got full banded for my Troll Warrior. He is only level 8. Has full
banded and a tunic that has same AC as a 1200 plat plate tunic. Very
interesting and cool. I can solo reds because of my armor. That is way to
good to pass up. Maybe at another time my necromancer will once again feed
off the skels of Nektulos Forrest.

-Kukok, Troll Warrior - Veeshan
